Package: pbanalysis
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2022-05-30
Title: Statistical Tools for Analysis of Disparities
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: ordinal, MASS, nnet, ggplot2
Description: Assessing disparity  by modeling counterfactuals via the Peters-Belson (ref) method.
  We provide a unified environment to carry out dispariy analysis for both random sampling data and population-based non-random sampling survey such as National Health and Nutrition Examination Survey (NHANES). The outcomes can be continuous, binary, and ordinal outcome.
